manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: It’s Essential. So Make It Cute and Comfy. Toss out the scratchy cloth mask and say goodbye to stuffy masks because KARIZMA Face Wardrobe wants to give your face a buttery soft hug instead! Contoured masks for protection… and generally being cute. And this soft mask also comes with adjustable ear loops for even more comfort and customization!

The First Rule Of Self-Care Club – Be Fussy With Your Fabrics Comfy and Cute. Let’s not suffer with chafing, itching and pain, or the hassle of removing our mask any longer, because this buttery-soft silk feel fabric is 92.5% polyester and 7.5% spandex! No one looks cute scratching and adjusting their mask all day! But Face Wardrobe is kind to skin and lets you get on with things without irritation. Love Fresh Air? Face Wardrobe Face Masks are non-stifling! The woven fabric, central seam placement, 3D contouring and 3-Way Stretch allows the mask to hug the nose and chin, and lets you talk without sticking to your mouth – or eating mask! As a result, you’ll probably find it more comfortable as a workout mask. 6 Colors Per Pack. This Face Wardrobe Mask Pack includes a Pink, 2x Grey, White, Beige and Black Face Mask so you can let your mask elevate your look! Measuring 13.5” ear to ear and 5.5” top to bottom they fit men, women and kids – but of course, measure first to make sure your beautiful face also loves the size of its new Face Wardrobe

KARIZMA – The Brand Our conversations, projects and collabs with stylists, influencers and celebrities inspire our creations, so you can feel equally beautiful, confident and ready to share your positive message to the world, too!

Wear It All Day Without Itching or Chafing. 6 Reusable Masks Did you know 3 million disposable masks get discarded every day! Ouch! But you, with your 4 soft cloth masks are in earth lovin’ heaven. Easy To Wash Face masks like this are best washed with care at 40 degrees with hand wash. They’re easy and fast to wash and dry, but don’t love bra hooks poking out in your laundry! Adjustable Ear Loops Face Wardrobe ear loops are the same buttery-soft fabric as the mask with the added benefit of adjustability for more comfort. Minimal ‘Maskne’ Fresh, moisture wicking, masks like this reduce maskne flares. And while such things can’t always be avoided, Face Wardrobe can help.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very cool product!
reviews.reviewText: I work in retail and I want to look cool as I wait on my customers as well as be safe--this is the perfect mask for most women!--makes you look like cat woman and keeps you cool and comfortable!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I Love the Earth Set
reviews.reviewText: I love these masks, especially the earth-toned set as they come in a range of natural colors, that may mimic a nice spectrum of skin tones. The material is soft and light. This is my second time purchasing this!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I love the colors. Sometimes they fold inward in my mouth and I have to pull it out over my nose to stretch it out again. I double mask at times, I wear a disposable mask over it. They are thin,soft, breathable and comfortable. I wash them in the washer and the colors have stayed the same.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Love these masks!!! Please don't ever stop making them. Best ever!!!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
Reviewed in the United States on August 1, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well made, looks like a mask to wear when dressing up.
reviews.reviewText: I saw this mask on a student and she looked so neat and polished. Although I could not touch her mask, I could tell that it appeared to lightweight and easier to breathe. I also like that it’s adjustable!I love this mask!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Colorful and serve their purpose.
reviews.reviewText: I like them. They fit well and look nice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable, soft, and fit perfectly
reviews.reviewText: Very pleased with these masks. Very soft and flexible while also covering the face adequately. Adjustable ear loops were a huge plus for me so my husband and I could share these masks. Love the colors and they fit perfectly. They seem to be pretty good quality but I wash my masks by hand and air dry so not sure how they would hold up in the wash.
